name: Shredded Apes Whey
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: $WHEY is the official utility token for the Shredded Apes Gym Club, providing a way to get access to our product line, which includes clothing, supplements, in-house services, grant discounts on secondary NFT collections, make in-game decisions, and also grants holders access to high-end perks. All of these will have burning mechanisms in place, in order to reduce the total circulting supply.
